column2: SELECT TOP # objid, ra, dec, petroR5#_r, petromag_r, BrightestObjin1#R5# FROM (SELECT objid, ra, dec, petroR5#_r, petromag_r, (SELECT max (p.petromag_r) FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (photoprimary.ra, photoprimary.dec, #*photoprimary.petroR5#_r) n JOIN photoprimary p ON p.objid = n.objid) as BrightestObjin1#R5# FROM photoprimary) f WHERE petromag_r > (BrightestObjin1#R5# - #)
